act_info.full_title: Highway Memorials for Fallen Police Officers Act, 2002, S.O. 2002, c. 26
act_info.citation: Highway Memorials for Fallen Police Officers Act, 2002, S.O. 2002, c. 26

content.content: 1. The Legislative Assembly may, by resolution, name bridges and other structures on the King’s Highway in memory of police officers who have died in the line of duty. 2002, c. 26, s. 1. 2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Act). 2002, c. 26, s. 2. 3. Omitted (enacts short title of this Act). 2002, c. 26, s. 3. _____________ Français
content.raw_html:
1. The Legislative Assembly may, by resolution, name bridges and other structures on the King’s Highway in memory of police officers who have died in the line of duty. 2002, c. 26, s. 1.

2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Act). 2002, c. 26, s. 2.

3. Omitted (enacts short title of this Act). 2002, c. 26, s. 3.

_____________
